# ====================
# Keep These Files (Documentation)
# ====================
# These are explicitly NOT ignored - just for reference:
# .claude/agents/*.md          - Agent definitions
# tools/article_search/*.py    - Search tools
# tools/README.md              - Tool documentation
# input/research_config.md     - Research configuration
# papers/papers_catalog.json   - Main catalog
# papers/SEARCH_REPORT.md      - Search reports
# sections/*.md                - Article sections
# FINAL_ARTICLE.md             - Final output
# README.md, CLAUDE.md         - Documentation
# MULTI_AGENT_PLAN.md         - Orchestration guide

# ====================
